{
  "stem": "21786.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And according to the Nuremberg laws, laws of the city of Nuremberg in 1935, a Jew was somebody whose grandparents were Jewish-- whether he was baptized or not, there was no exception.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So that in the [NON-ENGLISH] were some-- especially two girls who were Roman Catholics, and suddenly they were-- they turned Zionist, they turned Jewish.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we started to learn Hebrew with a tremendous speed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was a schaliach there from Israel-- from Palestine, sorry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] His name was Tzvi, forgot the last name.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he was teaching Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was teaching [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he took me as a kind of private project, so that I was studying Hebrew for about five-- four or five hours a day.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were being taught what's happening in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we were singing Hebrew songs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the rest of my Hebrew, which is still within me-- it depends on the songs.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I still know about, I would say, minimum 50 of Hebrew songs, and I can translate them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I-- as I mentioned, I met Eva, and we fell in love, being very young.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we became very courageous-- probably very stupid, also.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Like we both had our stars on just hooks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we unhooked the star and went together to a movie, which was forbidden, or to the part of the city which was forbidden, or took a streetcar to the edge of the city and went through the woods-- which, naturally, was forbidden.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But we were not caught.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Our usual place where we met, and when we simply dated, was the old Jewish cemetery, where we simply were alone.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And it was a nice solitude, sitting on the grave of the great Rabbi Low.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
